    "description": "<strong>Planet Zionx, Year 2068, its inhabitants are threatened by an emperor, come to their rescue by offering them food or sleep for example...</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357510/extras/eca8f092fcb9837291da70da94cb7bd0.avif?t=1687939887\" width=454 height=96 /></span></h2><br>Discover ROMPICHE-8 in full version ! Initially developed for the Gamejam Advance, ROMPICHE-8 is an action-adventure game with an absurd sense of humor in which you play as a robot in charge of bringing peace and rest to the planet Zionx.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357510/extras/db549620c1c26a649a47d28680f971eb.poster.avif?t=1687939887\" width=500 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357510/extras/db549620c1c26a649a47d28680f971eb.webm?t=1687939887\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357510/extras/db549620c1c26a649a47d28680f971eb.mp4?t=1687939887\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><br>In a gameplay inspired by the FPS of the 90s, you are over-equipped with rest material : <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Pillows (for sleeping)<br></li><li> Sandwiches (to eat)<br></li><li> And many other weapons ...</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Great for a good night of sleep !</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357510/extras/6714ea0dd53a3665ca2d487220715b87.avif?t=1687939887\" width=454 height=96 /></span></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357510/extras/813a20732be280ccf549021e546b7838.poster.avif?t=1687939887\" width=498 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357510/extras/813a20732be280ccf549021e546b7838.webm?t=1687939887\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357510/extras/813a20732be280ccf549021e546b7838.mp4?t=1687939887\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Create your own levels with the MIAMO editor, for increased replayability, then share them with the world on Steam Workshop!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357510/extras/de0edf1e1c54d27a65f6d68622999d02.avif?t=1687939887\" width=454 height=96 /></span></h2><br>Ready for the sandwich race? Discover the different online cooperative and versus modes of ROMPICHE-8!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Modes Planned For Launch </h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Playing the campaign in online coop<br></li><li> Race in a competitive game mode !</li></ul>",
